  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/091e921aed10d0a0c21efb372b092e0b.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/091e921aed10d0a0c21efb372b092e0b.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Run Your Own Sushi Restaurant</i></h2>Manage an otherworldly sushi shokudo in a mysterious world. Indulge the taste buds of your customers with strange sushi dishes, while getting upgrades to expand your business and make it more efficient and profitable. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/f6f3f41d531b6f5f58a55eb52cc8da03.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/f6f3f41d531b6f5f58a55eb52cc8da03.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Turn cute monsters into appetizing dishes!</i></h2>The caves are home to a number of peculiar and charming creatures. Collect precious ingredients from these monsters, and unlock a wide range of distinctive recipes to satisfy your customers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/fce3e78b336524ff5a2167bc7563a2ce.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/fce3e78b336524ff5a2167bc7563a2ce.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Atmospheric 2.5D Art</i></h2>Enjoy your restaurant-management experience in a 2.5D environment, featuring charming hand-drawn art.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/7cf99851f071939c9223120fe861bf5d.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/7cf99851f071939c9223120fe861bf5d.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>In Pursuit of the Legendary Chawanmushi!</i></h2>Unlock the coveted, mysterious dish. Fulfill your dream and satisfy the wishes of a weird and wacky deity!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/d539bd15e9d163d6ea5795345084ce19.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/d539bd15e9d163d6ea5795345084ce19.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
